       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI94500.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI94500.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Aprovaçăo de Férias                                        *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI94500         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD7001 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5303 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV9450.
       COPY COCV9451.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.
       COPY ARCL0039.
       COPY ETCL0002.
       COPY AQCW0005.
       COPY VIAL1000.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            SWITCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  SW-SWITCH.
           05 SW-CURSOR                  PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
              88 SW-CURSOR-NONE                    VALUE '0'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-1                       VALUE '1'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT7001 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT7001'.
           05 CON-COVT5303 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT5303'.
           05 CON-A        PIC X(02) VALUE 'A'.
           05 CON-N        PIC X(02) VALUE 'N'.
           05 CON-S        PIC X(02) VALUE 'S'.
           05 CON-SEP      PIC X(01) VALUE '-'.
           05 CON-SEP1     PIC X(01) VALUE '/'.
           05 CON-01       PIC X(02) VALUE '01'.
           05 CON-02       PIC X(02) VALUE '02'.
           05 CON-03       PIC X(02) VALUE '03'.
           05 CON-04       PIC X(02) VALUE '04'.
           05 CON-05       PIC X(02) VALUE '05'.
           05 CON-06       PIC X(02) VALUE '06'.
           05 CON-07       PIC X(02) VALUE '07'.
           05 CON-08       PIC X(02) VALUE '08'.
           05 CON-09       PIC X(02) VALUE '09'.
           05 CON-10       PIC X(02) VALUE '10'.
           05 CON-11       PIC X(02) VALUE '11'.
           05 CON-12       PIC X(02) VALUE '12'.
           05 CON-13       PIC X(02) VALUE '13'.
           05 CON-14       PIC X(02) VALUE '14'.
           05 CON-15       PIC X(02) VALUE '15'.
           05 CON-16       PIC X(02) VALUE '16'.
           05 CON-17       PIC X(02) VALUE '17'.
           05 CON-18       PIC X(02) VALUE '18'.
           05 CON-19       PIC X(02) VALUE '19'.
           05 CON-20       PIC X(02) VALUE '20'.
           05 CON-21       PIC X(02) VALUE '21'.
           05 CON-22       PIC X(02) VALUE '22'.
           05 CON-23       PIC X(02) VALUE '23'.
           05 CON-24       PIC X(02) VALUE '24'.
           05 CON-25       PIC X(02) VALUE '25'.
           05 CON-26       PIC X(02) VALUE '26'.
           05 CON-27       PIC X(02) VALUE '27'.
           05 CON-28       PIC X(02) VALUE '28'.
           05 CON-29       PIC X(02) VALUE '29'.
           05 CON-30       PIC X(02) VALUE '30'.
           05 CON-31       PIC X(02) VALUE '31'.
           05 CON-99       PIC X(02) VALUE '99'.
           05 WS-QUO       PIC 9(04).
           05 WS-RES       PIC 9(04).
           05 WS-ANO-X     PIC X(04).
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-ANO-X.
              10 WS-ANO-9  PIC 9(04).

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-ULT-DIA-MES        PIC   X(02).
           05 WS-O-PROPRIO          PIC   X(03)     VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-A                  PIC  S9(05)     COMP-3.
           05 WS-N                  PIC  S9(05)     COMP-3.
           05 WS-HORAS              PIC  S9(10)V99  COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-DTMESANO               PIC  X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DTMESANO.
              10 WS-DTMESANO-ANO        PIC  X(04)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-DTMESANO-FILL1      PIC  X(01)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-DTMESANO-MES        PIC  X(02)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-DTMESANO-FILL2      PIC  X(01)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-DTMESANO-DIA        PIC  X(02)  VALUE SPACES.

           05 WS-PERIODO                PIC  X(07)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-PERIODO.
              10 WS-PERIODO-ANO         PIC  X(04)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-PERIODO-SEP         PIC  X(01)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-PERIODO-MES         PIC  X(02)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DFERIAS-MIN-PER        PIC  X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DFERIAS-MAX-PER        PIC  X(10)  VALUE SPACES.

           05 WS-DATA-ULT          PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DATA-ULT.
              10 WS-DATA-ULT-ANO   PIC X(04).
              10 WS-DATA-ULT-SEP1  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DATA-ULT-MES   PIC X(02).
              10 WS-DATA-ULT-SEP2  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DATA-ULT-DIA   PIC X(02).

           05 WS-DATA-VER          PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DATA-VER.
              10 WS-DATA-VER-ANO   PIC X(04).
              10 WS-DATA-VER-SEP1  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DATA-VER-MES   PIC X(02).
              10 WS-DATA-VER-SEP2  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DATA-VER-DIA   PIC X(02).

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI94500'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *              DECLARACOES DE CURSORES DB2                     *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       01  WS-CURSOR-VARS.
           05 WS-CIDEMP-MIN             PIC  X(03) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CIDEMP-MAX             PIC  X(03) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DFERIAS-MIN            PIC  X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DFERIAS-MAX            PIC  X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CIDEMP                 PIC  X(03) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DFERIAS                PIC  X(10) VALUE SPACES.

           EXEC SQL
            DECLARE CURART01 CURSOR FOR
            SELECT CIDEMP
                 , SUBSTR(CHAR(DFERIAS), 1, 7)
            FROM COVT7001
            WHERE CIDEMP   >= :WS-CIDEMP-MIN
              AND CIDEMP   <= :WS-CIDEMP-MAX

              AND CIDEMP   <> :WS-O-PROPRIO

              AND DFERIAS  >= :WS-DFERIAS-MIN
              AND DFERIAS  <= :WS-DFERIAS-MAX

              AND CIDEMP   >= :COCD7001-CIDEMP

            GROUP BY CIDEMP, SUBSTR(CHAR(DFERIAS), 1, 7)
            ORDER BY CIDEMP, SUBSTR(CHAR(DFERIAS), 1, 7)
           END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI94500         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA'  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT TO VIAL0015-CAMPOS-CHAVE
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV9450-MSG.
           MOVE COCV9450-ASE               TO COCV9451-ASE.
      *
           INITIALIZE WS-VARIAVEIS
                      COCV9451-ADE          REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                                 ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE COCV9450-ADE                TO COCV9451-ADE.
      *
           PERFORM 2010-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2019-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2021-OBTER-USER
                 THRU 2021-OBTER-USER-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2020-OPEN
                 THRU 2029-OPEN-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2030-FETCH
                 THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF DB2-OK
               PERFORM 2040-CONTINUA
                  THRU 2049-CONTINUA-EXIT
             ELSE
               COMPUTE COCV9451-DIMINUI-LENGTH =
                       COCV9451-INDICE-INVERSO *
                       COCV9451-LENGTH-OCCUR
               COMPUTE COCV9451-LENGTH =
                       COCV9451-LENGTH -
                       COCV9451-DIMINUI-LENGTH

               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV9451-IDFUN-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CIDEMP-VAZIO
                      TO COCV9451-IDFUN-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV9451-IDFUN-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2070-CLOSE
              THRU 2079-CLOSE-EXIT.
      *
       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2021-OBTER-USER
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2021-OBTER-USER.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2021-OBTER-USER' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
      *--- LER COT53_PESSOAS com USER para obter o NTRABALHADOR
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I    TO COCD5303-CUTILIZA.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT NTRABALHADOR
                  , GNOME
                  , CEMPRESA
               INTO :COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR
                  , :COCD5303-GNOME
                  , :COCD5303-CEMPRESA
               FROM COVT5303_PESSOAS
            WHERE CUTILIZA = :COCD5303-CUTILIZA
            FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5303               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF DB2-OK
                MOVE COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR TO WS-O-PROPRIO
             ELSE
                MOVE SPACES                TO WS-O-PROPRIO
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2021-OBTER-USER-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2010-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2010-VALIDACOES.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2010-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCV9450-ANO        ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  COCV9450-ANO          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE COCV9450-ANO             TO COCV9451-ANO.
           MOVE COCV9450-XDESCANO        TO COCV9451-XDESCANO.
           MOVE COCV9450-IDFUN           TO COCV9451-IDFUN.
           MOVE COCV9450-XDESCIDFUN      TO COCV9451-XDESCIDFUN.
      *
       2019-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2020-OPEN
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2020-OPEN.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCV9451-D-IDFUN(1) ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  COCV9451-D-IDFUN(1)   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'COCV9450-ANO     ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (2)
              MOVE  COCV9450-ANO       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE COCV9450-IDFUN-PAG     TO COCD7001-CIDEMP.
      *
           IF COCV9450-IDFUN = SPACES
              MOVE SPACES              TO WS-CIDEMP-MIN
              MOVE '999'               TO WS-CIDEMP-MAX
           ELSE
              MOVE COCV9450-IDFUN      TO WS-CIDEMP-MIN
              MOVE COCV9450-IDFUN      TO WS-CIDEMP-MAX
           END-IF.
      *
           IF COCV9450-ANO = SPACES
              MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN   TO WS-DFERIAS-MIN
              MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MAX   TO WS-DFERIAS-MAX
           ELSE
              IF COCV9450-MES = SPACES
                 MOVE COCV9450-ANO        TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO
                 MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DTMESANO-FILL1
                 MOVE CON-01              TO WS-DTMESANO-MES
                 MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DTMESANO-FILL2
                 MOVE CON-01              TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
                 MOVE WS-DTMESANO         TO WS-DFERIAS-MIN

                 MOVE COCV9450-ANO        TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO
                 MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DTMESANO-FILL1
                 MOVE CON-12              TO WS-DTMESANO-MES
                 MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DTMESANO-FILL2
                 MOVE CON-31              TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
                 MOVE WS-DTMESANO         TO WS-DFERIAS-MAX
              ELSE
                 MOVE COCV9450-ANO        TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO
                 MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DTMESANO-FILL1
                 MOVE COCV9450-MES        TO WS-DTMESANO-MES
                 MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DTMESANO-FILL2
                 MOVE CON-01              TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
                 MOVE WS-DTMESANO         TO WS-DFERIAS-MIN

                 MOVE COCV9450-ANO        TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO
                 MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DTMESANO-FILL1
                 MOVE COCV9450-MES        TO WS-DTMESANO-MES
                 MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DTMESANO-FILL2
                 MOVE CON-01              TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
                 MOVE WS-DTMESANO         TO WS-DATA-VER

                 PERFORM 2180-VER-ULT-DIA
                    THRU 2180-VER-ULT-DIA-EXIT
                 MOVE WS-ULT-DIA-MES      TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA

                 MOVE WS-DTMESANO         TO WS-DFERIAS-MAX
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
             OPEN CURART01
           END-EXEC.
      *
           MOVE CON-COVT7001               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
       2029-OPEN-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2030-FETCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2030-FETCH.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2030-FETCH' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           EXEC SQL
              FETCH CURART01
              INTO  :COCD7001-CIDEMP
                  , :WS-PERIODO
           END-EXEC.
      *
           MOVE CON-COVT7001               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
       2039-FETCH-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2040-CONTINUA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2040-CONTINUA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2040-CONTINUA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO COCV9451-INDICE.

           PERFORM 2050-TRATA-OCCURS
              THRU 2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT
             UNTIL NOT DB2-OK
                OR COCV9451-PAGINA-CHEIA
                OR NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS.

      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF NOT COCV9451-PAGINA-CHEIA
               COMPUTE COCV9451-INDICE-INVERSO EQUAL
                       COCV9451-INDICE-INVERSO - COCV9451-INDICE
               COMPUTE COCV9451-DIMINUI-LENGTH EQUAL
                       COCV9451-INDICE-INVERSO * COCV9451-LENGTH-OCCUR
               COMPUTE COCV9451-LENGTH EQUAL COCV9451-LENGTH -
                       COCV9451-DIMINUI-LENGTH
                SET  VIAL0002-FIM-CONSULTA TO TRUE
              END-IF
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                SET VIAL0002-FIM-CONSULTA TO TRUE
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
       2049-CONTINUA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2050-TRATA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2050-TRATA-OCCURS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
             MOVE '2050-TRATA-OCCURS'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
             MOVE 'COCV9451-INDICE       '     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
             MOVE  COCV9451-INDICE             TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
             PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           ADD  1                 TO COCV9451-INDICE.

           MOVE COCD7001-CIDEMP
             TO COCV9451-D-IDFUN(COCV9451-INDICE).
           MOVE CON-SEP1
             TO WS-PERIODO-SEP.
           MOVE WS-PERIODO
             TO COCV9451-D-PERIODO(COCV9451-INDICE).
           MOVE WS-PERIODO-ANO
             TO COCV9451-D-CANO(COCV9451-INDICE).
           MOVE WS-PERIODO-MES
             TO COCV9451-D-CMES(COCV9451-INDICE).
           MOVE COCD7001-CIDEMP
             TO COCV9451-D-CIDEMP(COCV9451-INDICE).

      *--- Formata limites de datas para periodo
           MOVE WS-PERIODO-ANO      TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO.
           MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DTMESANO-FILL1.
           MOVE WS-PERIODO-MES      TO WS-DTMESANO-MES.
           MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DTMESANO-FILL2.
           MOVE CON-01              TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA.
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO         TO WS-DFERIAS-MIN-PER.

           MOVE WS-PERIODO-ANO      TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO.
           MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DTMESANO-FILL1.
           MOVE WS-PERIODO-MES      TO WS-DTMESANO-MES.
           MOVE CON-SEP             TO WS-DTMESANO-FILL2.

           IF WS-PERIODO-MES = CON-01
           OR WS-PERIODO-MES = CON-03
           OR WS-PERIODO-MES = CON-05
           OR WS-PERIODO-MES = CON-07
           OR WS-PERIODO-MES = CON-08
           OR WS-PERIODO-MES = CON-10
           OR WS-PERIODO-MES = CON-12
              MOVE CON-31           TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
           END-IF.

           IF WS-PERIODO-MES = CON-04
           OR WS-PERIODO-MES = CON-06
           OR WS-PERIODO-MES = CON-09
           OR WS-PERIODO-MES = CON-11
              MOVE CON-30           TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
           END-IF.

           IF WS-PERIODO-MES = CON-02
              MOVE WS-PERIODO-ANO TO WS-ANO-X
              DIVIDE WS-ANO-9 BY 4 GIVING WS-QUO REMAINDER WS-RES
              IF WS-RES = ZEROS
                 MOVE CON-29        TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
              ELSE
                 MOVE CON-28        TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           MOVE WS-DTMESANO         TO WS-DFERIAS-MAX-PER.

      *--- Dias aprovados
      *    MOVE ZEROS TO WS-A.
      *    PERFORM 2021-VER-A THRU 2021-VER-A-EXIT.
      *    IF WS-A > ZEROS
      *       MOVE CON-S
      *         TO COCV9451-D-A(COCV9451-INDICE)
      *    ELSE
      *       MOVE CON-N
      *         TO COCV9451-D-A(COCV9451-INDICE)
      *    END-IF.
      *--- Dias năo aprovados
           MOVE ZEROS TO WS-N.
           PERFORM 2022-VER-N THRU 2022-VER-N-EXIT.
           IF WS-N > ZEROS
              MOVE CON-S
                TO COCV9451-D-N(COCV9451-INDICE)
           ELSE
              MOVE CON-N
                TO COCV9451-D-N(COCV9451-INDICE)
           END-IF.
      *--- Verifica filtro de férias aprovadas
           IF COCV9450-FERPORAPR = CON-N
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              IF  COCV9450-FERPORAPR = CON-S
              AND COCV9451-D-N(COCV9451-INDICE) = CON-N
                  PERFORM 2025-LIMPA-LINHA
                     THRU 2025-LIMPA-LINHA-EXIT
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             PERFORM 2030-FETCH
                THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
       2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2021-VER-A
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *2021-VER-A.
      *
      *    IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
      *       MOVE '2021-VER-A' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
      *       PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
      *          THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
      *    END-IF.
      *
      *    EXEC SQL
      *     SELECT IFNULL(COUNT(*), 0)
      *       INTO :WS-A
      *     FROM COVT7001
      *     WHERE CIDEMP   = :COCD7001-CIDEMP
      *       AND DFERIAS  >= :WS-DFERIAS-MIN-PER
      *       AND DFERIAS  <= :WS-DFERIAS-MAX-PER
      *       AND CSITU    =  :CON-A
      *    END-EXEC.
      *
      *2021-VER-A-EXIT.
      *    EXIT.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2022-VER-N
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2022-VER-N.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2022-VER-N' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           EXEC SQL
            SELECT IFNULL(COUNT(*), 0)
              INTO :WS-N
            FROM COVT7001
            WHERE CIDEMP   = :COCD7001-CIDEMP
              AND DFERIAS  >= :WS-DFERIAS-MIN-PER
              AND DFERIAS  <= :WS-DFERIAS-MAX-PER
              AND CSITU    =  :CON-N
           END-EXEC.

       2022-VER-N-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2180-VER-ULT-DIA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2180-VER-ULT-DIA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2180-VER-ULT-DIA ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ZEROS TO WS-ULT-DIA-MES.

           INITIALIZE VIAL1000-AREA-COMUNICACAO
                                   REPLACING  NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                         ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           MOVE '09'             TO VIAL1000-COD-PROCESSO.
           MOVE WS-DATA-VER      TO AQCW0005-DTX10
           PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8
              THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8-EXIT
           MOVE AQCW0005-DT98    TO VIAL1000-DAT-INPUT1

           PERFORM VIAP1000-ROTINA-DATAS
              THRU VIAP1000-EXIT.

           IF VIAL1000-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE VIAL1000-DAT-RES-ED TO WS-DATA-ULT
              MOVE WS-DATA-ULT-DIA     TO WS-ULT-DIA-MES
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAL1000-IND-ERROS TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAL1000-COD-ERRO-GRAVE TO
                                     VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2180-VER-ULT-DIA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2025-LIMPA-LINHA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2025-LIMPA-LINHA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2025-LIMPA-LINHA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE COCV9451-D-IDFUN(COCV9451-INDICE)
                      COCV9451-D-PERIODO(COCV9451-INDICE)
                      COCV9451-D-CANO(COCV9451-INDICE)
                      COCV9451-D-CMES(COCV9451-INDICE)
                      COCV9451-D-CIDEMP(COCV9451-INDICE)
                      COCV9451-D-N(COCV9451-INDICE).

           SUBTRACT 1 FROM COCV9451-INDICE.

       2025-LIMPA-LINHA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2070-CLOSE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2070-CLOSE.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2070-CLOSE' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           EXEC SQL
               CLOSE CURART01
           END-EXEC.
      *
       2079-CLOSE-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF COCV9450-NMAXLIST EQUAL ZEROES
              MOVE VIAL0001-CAPLIC         TO ARCL0039-CAPLIC
              MOVE VIAL0001-COPCAO         TO ARCL0039-COPCAO
              PERFORM ARCR0039-NMAXLIST
                 THRU ARCR0039-NMAXLIST-EXIT

              IF ETCL0002-ABEND-DB2
                 MOVE ETCL0002-TABLE-NAME  TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME
                 MOVE ETCL0002-SQLCA       TO VIAL0002-SQLCA
              END-IF

              MOVE ARCL0039-NMAXLIST       TO COCV9451-NMAXLIST
           ELSE
              MOVE COCV9450-NMAXLIST       TO COCV9451-NMAXLIST
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV9451-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV9451-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV9451-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE COCV9451-INDICE            TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.
      *
       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCR0039 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP1000.
           COPY VIAP0016.
           COPY AQCP0005.
